-So, what did everyone think?

21:05.264 --> 21:06.533
It was the finest play

21:06.566 --> 21:08.034
that any of us have ever seen.

21:08.067 --> 21:10.102
-Good job, guys.
-So good.

21:10.136 --> 21:11.771
And we'd like to see it again
right now.

21:11.804 --> 21:13.239
-What?
-No.

21:13.272 --> 21:14.807
What? I lie,
and then I double down.

21:14.841 --> 21:16.409
I've made that very clear.

